{"tid":1847194,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"要封關唔可以靠政府，但黎明行動就係迫政府去做嘢，明顯係冇用","createTime":"2020-01-28T03:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T02:41:54.000Z","uid":158270,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e4d7e6a66be1a68be0b3c698c4d3cfbd9116fcc","tid":1847194,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:17:24.000Z","msg":"先唔講黎明行動失敗率極高，我假設佢成功阻全香港人人返工一日，行動大成功，政府都係唔會封關。<br />\n而且壞處係阻住醫療物資由外國入嚟香港，明顯弊大於利。<br />\n<br />\n參考粉嶺一役，我哋要封關，大家就應對準關口，用水泥又好石屎又好炸橋又好封咗個關去。我唔見粉嶺人會用罷工去迫政府唔好起隔離營，政府睬你都on9。"},{"pid":"6d36772c06082f951c969e7f5c3add5568aef2c2","tid":1847194,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:28:45.000Z","msg":"而且罷工&mdash;&mdash;政府回應&mdash;&mdash;封關同預告封關有咩分別？武漢市政府一話第二日封城，啲人嗰晚就已經走晒出嚟大逃亡。依家就算政府聽民意去封，只會引晒啲人過嚟。"},{"pid":"c1009285a307e18809be0f510f385623b5459c1d","tid":1847194,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"點解要幫政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要攬炒既咩"},{"pid":"50f4c66e5c4f8665a5538c5a511c54ef6a70d581","tid":1847194,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1009285a307e18809be0f510f385623b5459c1d","tid":1847194,"uid":123615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"點解要幫政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係要攬炒既咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"點解要幫自己係幫政府？<br />\n政府唔係賣香港人㗎咩？"},{"pid":"cd076fbc4c75a4839e94d19d8707e485631ebd40","tid":1847194,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:14:00.000Z","msg":"[老豆搵仔] 第一粒炸彈會係非鐵路連接嘅口岸<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1847144\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1847144</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ee0e328016e0c4ebacce4e0710b9586adb6d9bbd","tid":1847194,"uid":3357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:14:53